cemail → 写槽 → unread notify","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":362,"content":"### 6.1 scheduleTick 与 voicemail","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":365,"content":"- 目标为 `cardKind=voicemail`：到点 **入栈/物化进信箱**（「N 分钟后信箱多一条」）；用户正在通话时仍写槽，不打断当前 CallSession。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]},{"file":"docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/07-壳嵌入与导出契约.md","matches":[{"lineNumber":122,"content":"| schedule / 外呼类（目标非 voicemail） | 真响铃 / CallIntent（经 EffectSink） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":123,"content":"| `attach_call_card` / `schedule_call_card` → **voicemail** | **不**经 Sink 写信箱；入 GenStack → plan 终态后 `VoicemailMaterializePipeline` |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":124,"content":"| `generateVoicemail`（Host 注入端口） | 引擎外 LLM/TTS；返回 text / audioRef；未注入则该条失败/跳过策略，不炸 Host |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":125,"content":"| `onVoicemailUnreadChanged`（Host 注入端口） | 壳 LED / 角标；**真源**仍在 `Profile.telephony.voicemails[]`（`deriveVoicemailHasUnread`） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":126,"content":"| ~~`create_voicemail`~~ | **已废弃**：校验 `VOICEMAIL_CREATE_EFFECT`；Executor / Sink **无**新写路径 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":132,"content":"时序：Executor 逻辑写盘意图 → Sink 媒介（若有）→ plan 终态 → **VoicemailMaterialize**（若栈非空）→ save。详见 [19 §6](./19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md)。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]},{"file":"docs/AI和人类/需求/08-内容校验规则.md","matches":[{"lineNumber":34,"content":"| `PLAYBACK_NO_ASSET` | error | playback_only 无 playbackClipId（**不含** `cardKind=voicemail`：留言靠物化，允许无 clip） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":36,"content":"## 2.1 语音留言（voicemail）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":38,"content":"真源：[语音留言改造需求](../里程碑/v2.0/语音留言改造需求.md) §3.1–§3.3；实现见 `validation/package/voicemail.ts`。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":42,"content":"| `VOICEMAIL_INTERACTION_MODE` | error | `cardKind=voicemail` 但 `interactionMode !== playback_only` |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":43,"content":"| `VOICEMAIL_ENTRY_MODE` | error | `cardKind=voicemail` 但 `entryMode !== mailbox_open` |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":44,"content":"| `VOICEMAIL_TOOL_POLICY` | error | `cardKind=voicemail` 但 toolPolicy 非 deny_all 等价 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":45,"content":"| `VOICEMAIL_ENTRY_KIND` | error | 非 voicemail 卡使用 `entryMode=mailbox_open` |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":46,"content":"| `VOICEMAIL_CREATE_EFFECT` | error | 包内仍出现废弃 Effect `create_voicemail`（须改 `attach_call_card` / `schedule_call_card` 指向 voicemail 卡）；对 cardRaw 扫描，schema 亦拒识该 effect 名 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]},{"file":"docs/AI和人类/需求/04-调试器界面需求.md","matches":[{"lineNumber":90,"content":"| **信箱列表** | 读 `Profile.telephony.voicemails[]`（真源）；展示 status / text 摘要 / audioRef |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":92,"content":"| **听完** | 以 `entryMode=mailbox_open` + `cardKind=voicemail` 的 `beginCall` 起会话（`playback_only`）；播完 / 跳过 → Outcome（`voicemail_listened` / `playback_completed` / `playback_skipped`）→ ExitSelector → 该卡 exits |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]},{"file":"docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md","matches":[{"lineNumber":20,"content":"  → （若 GenStack 非空）VoicemailMaterializePipeline（plan 终态之后；外置生成端口）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":30,"content":"- **`cardKind=voicemail` 永不进 `Board.pending`**；进信箱靠 attach/schedule 分流 + 物化（见 §8.4–§8.5）。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":43,"content":"  | { kind: \"mailbox_open\"; agentId: string; voicemailId: string; cardId: string }","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":44,"content":"  // 信箱打开：听已物化留言；Resolver / beginCall 绑定该 voicemail 卡（entryMode=mailbox_open）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":47,"content":"**听留言路径（钉死）：** 用户/调试打开信箱条目 → `mailbox_open` → `beginCall`（`frozenCard` = 该 `cardKind=voicemail` 卡，`interactionMode=playback_only`）→ 播槽内 text/audioRef → Outcome（`voicemail_listened` / `playback_completed` / `playback_skipped` 等）→ ExitSelector → 该卡 `exits`。**不推荐**壳自播完只打 flag、Host 另写无 Session 的 exits 捷径。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":63,"content":"3. `mailbox_open`：按信箱槽 `voicemailId` + `cardId` 绑定该 **`cardKind=voicemail`** Definition；**不**从 `Board.pending` 挑选；Session 强制 `playback_only` + `entryMode=mailbox_open`。播槽内已物化内容。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":67,"content":"   - **禁止**把 `cardKind=voicemail` 解析为待接通剧情卡（voicemail 永不在 pending）。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":187,"content":"| `attach_call_card` | **分流**：目标非 voicemail → Profile.Board 增加 pending；目标 voicemail → push VoicemailGenStack（**不写 Board**） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":189,"content":"| `schedule_call_card` | **分流**：目标非 voicemail → 写入 once intent，到点 `agent_outbound`；目标 voicemail → once intent，到点入栈/物化进信箱（**非**外呼） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":191,"content":"| ~~`create_voicemail`~~ | **废弃**：校验拒绝；运行时不执行新写。旧 stub 读路径可过渡，不得作为新写真源 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":206,"content":"### 8.4 attach / schedule 对 voicemail 的分流","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":212,"content":"| 非 `voicemail` | 写 `Board.pending` | `agent_outbound` 响铃语义（现状） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":213,"content":"| `voicemail` | push **VoicemailGenStack**；**禁止**写 Board | 入栈/物化进信箱；**禁止** `agent_outbound` |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":217,"content":"- 把 voicemail Instance 写入 `callCards.board.byAgent.*.pending`","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":221,"content":"### 8.5 VoicemailMaterializePipeline（plan 终态之后）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":227,"content":"1. 出栈；加载卡定义；确认 `cardKind=voicemail`","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":229,"content":"3. 调用注入端口 `generateVoicemail(input)`（引擎外 LLM/TTS；Studio Manual 可注入假实现）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":230,"content":"4. 写 `Profile.telephony.voicemails[]`（text 与/或 audioRef）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":236,"content":"generateVoicemail?(input: {","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":264,"content":"- 目标 **非** voicemail：越过后生成 `agent_outbound`（外呼响铃）。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":265,"content":"- 目标 **是** voicemail：越过后入 GenStack / 物化进信箱（**不是**外呼）；见 §8.4。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":271,"content":"以实现级 Host 为准，见 [19 §1.2](../技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md)。需求摘要：`resolve` / `beginCall` / `endCall` / `advanceClock` / `saveProfile` / `getSnapshot` / `getRecentLogs`。语音留言相关可注入：`generateVoicemail` / `onVoicemailUnreadChanged`（见 §8.5）。**禁止**依赖 React；**禁止**引擎持 LLM Key。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]},{"file":"docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md","matches":[{"lineNumber":21,"content":"type CardKind = \"free\" | \"story\" | \"system\" | \"schedule\" | \"voicemail\"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":23,"content":"type EntryMode = \"inbound_user_dial\" | \"outbound_auto\" | \"either\" | \"mailbox_open\"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":50,"content":"| `voicemail` | **语音留言卡**：进信箱、听完走本卡 exits；**永不**进入 `Board.pending`；不可经普通 `user_dial` / `agent_outbound` 解析为待接通剧情卡 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":52,"content":"**`voicemail` 强制组合（校验 error，Studio 锁定 disable）：**","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":57,"content":"| `entryMode` | **仅** `mailbox_open`（界面文案「信箱打开」） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":60,"content":"`context` 对 voicemail 仍是剧情/生成合同：物化端口消费 `speakableBrief` / `privateBrief` / `objective` 等；若 `assets.playbackClipId` 已有成品片，物化可跳过 LLM 直接引用。详见 [语音留言改造需求 §3](../里程碑/v2.0/语音留言改造需求.md)。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":69,"content":"| `mailbox_open` | **信箱打开**：用户/调试从信箱条目进入听留言；**仅**与 `cardKind=voicemail` 配对 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":233,"content":"| `attach_call_card` | `agentId`, `cardId`, `activation?` | 见下方 **挂卡分流表**（普通卡 → Board.pending；voicemail → 进信箱生成栈） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":235,"content":"| `schedule_call_card` | `agentId`, `cardId`, `delay: { minMs, maxMs }` | 见下方 **挂卡分流表**（普通卡 → 延迟外呼；voicemail → 延迟进信箱） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":237,"content":"| ~~`create_voicemail`~~ | — | **已废弃**：校验 error / Schema 拒识；Studio 下拉删除。留言一律用 `cardKind=voicemail` + `attach_call_card` / `schedule_call_card` |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":254,"content":"| Effect | 目标为普通卡（非 voicemail） | 目标为 `cardKind=voicemail` |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":261,"content":"未知 `effect` 名：校验失败，运行时拒绝执行。包内若仍出现 `create_voicemail`：校验 **error**，并指引改为 `attach_call_card` / `schedule_call_card` 指向 `cardKind=voicemail` 卡。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":456,"content":"  | \"voicemail_listened\"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]}],"totalLines":60,"totalMatchedLines":60,"clientTruncated":false,"ripgrepTruncated":false}}}}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-84d39c63-8907-48a7-ab7a-59a76b52ef11-16\nfc_54a84ac9-8c0d-93a7-970e-935133fccf85_4","startedAtMs":"1784792468722","completedAtMs":"1784792468889"},"model_call_id":"2b71313b-a89a-48db-b7fc-d60c320a4473-3-8n00","session_id":"d50e5eff-861e-4156-870f-dc415b750581","timestamp_ms":1784792468886}
